"\"@1750213766.431961072\"\",\"\"description\"\":\"\"failed to connect to all addresses\"\",\"\"file\"\":\"\"src/core/ext/filters/client_channel/lb_policy/pick_first/pick_first.cc\"\",\"\"file_line\"\":394,\"\"grpc_status\"\":14}]}\"\"\\n>\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,recommendationservice,frontend-0,recommendationservice-0,/hipstershop.RecommendationService/ListRecommendations,2,\"_InactiveRpcError: <_InactiveRpcError of RPC that terminated with:\\n\\tstatus = StatusCode.UNAVAILABLE\\n\\tdetails = \"\"failed to connect to all addresses\"\"\\n\\tdebug_error_string = \"\"{\"\"created\"\":\"\"@1750213790.602029114\"\",\"\"description\"\":\"\"Failed to pick subchannel\"\",\"\"file\"\":\"\"src/core/ext/filters/client_channel/client_channel.cc\"\",\"\"file_line\"\":3948,\"\"referenced_errors\"\":[{\"\"created\"\":\"\"@1750213766.431961072\"\",\"\"description\"\":\"\"failed to connect to all addresses\"\",\"\"file\"\":\"\"src/core/ext/filters/client_channel/lb_policy/pick_first/pick_first.cc\"\",\"\"file_line\"\":394,\"\"grpc_status\"\":14}]}\"\"\\n>\",出现次数:1\n", "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-18T02:10:11Z to 2025-06-18T02:30:11Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-18 02:10:11+00:00 to 2025-06-18 02:30:11+00:00"}, "trace_data_collected": true, "trace_analysis_findings": "经过对调用链数据的分析，我们发现如下异常调用链和错误状态：\n\n### 延迟显著性\n我们计算了异常延迟倍数，以识别显著的延迟瓶颈。在此期间，以下调用链表现出了显著的延迟：\n\n1. **呼叫链 Checkout → Cart**\n   - `normal_avg_duration`: 1952.24 ms\n   - `anomaly_avg_duration`: 18587.5 ms\n   - 延迟倍数: 9.52 (显著延迟)\n\n2. **呼叫链 Cart → Redis**\n   - `normal_avg_duration`: 1553.16 ms\n   - `anomaly_avg_duration`: 12597.52 ms\n   - 延迟倍数: 8.11 (显著延迟)\n\n### 错误状态分析\n对故障期间的错误状态组合进行了审查，发现如下错误状态：\n\n1. **前端服务 Frontend**\n   - Frequent `HTTP status code: 500` 错误，表明该服务请求内部出现错误。\n\n2. **ProductCatalogService**\n   - 多次出现 `connection refused` 错误，表明该服务无法连接，可能服务挂了或不可用。\n\n3. **RecommendationService**\n   - 多次出现 `StatusCode.UNAVAILABLE` 错误，表明推荐服务连接失败。\n\n### 根因定位与传播路径\n根据调用链拓扑结构，最下游异常的组件可能是根因：\n\n- **RecommendationService** 是异常的源头，因为多次出现连接失败代码 `UNAVAILABLE`，导致上游的服务都出现故障。\n- **ProductCatalogService**的多次连接拒绝情况也表明产品服务在这个问题期间可能出现不可用状态。\n\n### 关键发现\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->RecommendationService\",\n    \"frontend->ProductCatalogService\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"RecommendationService\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"多次出现 'StatusCode.UNAVAILABLE' 错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"频繁的 'connection refused' 错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"延迟倍数高达 9.52\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些是当前故障情况的主要异常点及可能的起因。这些信息可以为深入的排错和解决问题提供指导。请根据发现进一步验证和排查。", "log_analysis_findings": "根据分析提供的日志数据，我们可以识别出两个主要的错误模式：\n\n1. **Port Misconfiguration 故障**:\n   - 日志中多次出现 \"connection refused\" 的字词。具体例子包括从 `frontend` 服务抱怨无法连接到某地址，这暗示目标服务的端口可能配置错误。\n   - 日志示例：`\"error\": \"could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.54.177:3550: connect: connection refused\\\"\"`\n   - 相关的服务和端口配置错误涉及到的服务是 `recommendationservice`。\n\n2. **服务连接故障**:\n   - 许多日志提及“failed to connect to all addresses”或者“failed to pick subchannel”，这通常与网络配置错误或服务实例不可用有关。\n   - 日志示例：`\"details = \\\"failed to connect to all addresses\\\"\"`, `\"debug_error_string = \\\"{...\\\"description\\\":\\\"Failed to pick subchannel\\\"...}\"`\n\n以下是相关的 JSON 输出格式，概要描述异常组件及其原因。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"connection refused\",\n    \"transport\",\n    \"Error while dialing\",\n    \"failed to connect to all addresses\",\n    \"failed to pick subchannel\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Port misconfiguration causing 'connection refused', and network/service configuration issues leading to 'failed to connect to all addresses'.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"\\\"error\\\": \\\"could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.54.177:3550: connect: connection refused\\\"\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Service connectivity failure 'failed to pick subchannel', with issues in network routing or instances availability.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"\\\"debug_error_string = \\\"{\\\"created\\\":\\\"@1750212612.851821677\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Failed to pick subchannel\\\",...}\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些日志表明，不仅仅是端口配置，还可能有服务实例或网络上的问题，需要进一步验证服务配置和网络参数。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据获取的数据，我们识别了一系列潜在的异常调用链和指标变化。下面是我们的初步分析：\n\n### 异常指标\n从 `anomaly_metrics` CSV 中提取的异常指标是：\n- `memory_usage`\n- `error_ratio`\n- `client_error_ratio`\n- `server_error_ratio`\n- `request`\n- `response`\n- `rrt_max`\n\n### 显著异常链和归因\n\n1. **Redis Pod 故障**\n   - **组件**: `redis-cart-0`\n   - **异常指标**: `rrt_max`\n   - **原因**: 该 Pod 的 `rrt_max` 增加显著，表明该数据库的响应时间突然增加。\n   - **证据**: `rrt_max` 中位数从 6022.0 增加到 2032.5，P99 变化从 80976.7 到 75449.02。\n\n2. **Frontend Service 故障**\n   - **组件**: `frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, `frontend-2`\n   - **异常指标**: `error_ratio`, `server_error_ratio`, `rrt_max`\n   - **原因**: 由于 `error_ratio` 和 `server_error_ratio` 的出现，表明前端服务多个实例在这一时间段内遇到了异常高的错误率。\n   - **证据**: `frontend-1` 和 `frontend-2` 的 `server_error_ratio` 从正常变为 41.97 和 42.6。 `frontend-0` 和 `frontend-1` 的 `rrt_max` 也显著增加。\n\n3. **Adservice Pod 故障**\n   - **组件**: `adservice-0`, `adservice-1`\n   - **异常指标**: `client_error_ratio`, `error_ratio`\n   - **原因**: 指标表明 Adservice 在这段时间内客户端请求错误率上升。\n   - **证据**: `client_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 的 P99 变化显著，分别从正常变为 5.86。\n\n### 输出形成\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"memory_usage\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"request\",\n    \"response\",\n    \"rrt_max\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod的rrt_max增大，响应时间增加。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从6022.0增加到2032.5，中位数变化显著。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"多个实例的error_ratio和server_error_ratio显著增加。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio在多个Pod显著增加，达到41.97到42.6。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"client_error_ratio和error_ratio显著增加，表明请求错误率上升。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"指标变化显著，P99变化达到5.86。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n请仔细验证这些假设和证据，以确认故障的根本原因。进一步分析可能需要查看调用链中的具体日志和上下文信息。"}
